agraph\" >* Warehouses - Expand storage capacity</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Compactors - Multiply factory output</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras/9e408a2a19c3a2a51ae578c36b28c8c4.avif?t=1739455097\" width=246 height=106 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💾 Quality of Life Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Auto-save system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Export/Import save files</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Zoom and pan controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Keyboard shortcuts for quick actions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Clear visual feedback for all actions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras/20558e7fa742c15af5be9204a2624f74.webp?t=1739455097\" width=231 height=62 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless Optimization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision matters in Idle Grid. Will you focus on maximizing factory output, research efficiency, or power generation? Create your own strategies and watch your industrial empire grow while you're away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for both active management and idle progression, Idle Grid offers a satisfying blend of strategic depth and incremental growth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras/776a0602d6aab24645cc38a7ceb647bb.poster.avif?t=1739455097\" width=288 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras/776a0602d6aab24645cc38a7ceb647bb.webm?t=1739455097\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras/776a0602d6aab24645cc38a7ceb647bb.mp4?t=1739455097\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras/c372b991f4f4c197722fa235dda34bc1.avif?t=1739455097\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2940220/extras_big/c372b991f4f4c197722fa235dda34bc1.avif?t=1739455097 width=800 height=472 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[incrementaldb_verification: MightyIdle355]</p>",
